<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CookHub | About Us</title>
    <!-- Font -->
    <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Plus Jakarta Sans' rel='stylesheet'>
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/da12da5f88.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <!-- CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../assets/styles/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../assets/styles/responsive.css">
    <script src="../js/loadHTML.js"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #fffaf0; 
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans';
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .about-main {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 80px auto 40px; /* margin-top: 80px để tránh bị header che */
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        .about-section {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .about-section h1, .about-section h2 {
            color: #FF7D00; /* Màu cam từ style.css */
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .about-section h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
        }
        .about-section h2 {
            font-size: 1.8em;
        }
        .about-section p {
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-size: 1em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .stats, .values, .team {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .stat-item, .value-item, .team-member {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 200px;
            background-color: #fff; /* Nền trắng */
            border: 1px solid #ddd; /* Viền nhẹ */
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .stat-item h3, .value-item h3, .team-member h3 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .stat-item p, .value-item p, .team-member p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }
        .value-item i {
            color: #FF7D00;
            font-size: 2em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .team-member img {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .stats, .values, .team {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Begin: Header -->
    <div class="header"></div>
    <!-- End: Header -->

    <!-- Begin: About Us Content -->
    <div class="about-main">
        <div class="about-section">
            <h1>Building CookHub with Love and Code</h1>
            <p>A project born from late-night coding sessions, endless debates, and a shared passion for food and technology.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-section">
            <h2>Our Story</h2>
            <p>CookHub began as a humble project for our Software Engineering course in 2025. We were a team of 6 students, each bringing our unique skills (and quirks) to the table, united by a single goal: to create a platform where food lovers could save, share, and discover recipes.</p>
            <p>From brainstorming sessions that turned into food debates (spoiler: Ly Na always won), to coding marathons that stretched until 2 a.m., we poured our hearts into this project. Despite the occasional bugs, missed deadlines, and Sohyun’s infamous “one last UI tweak” that took 3 days, we made it through—stronger as a team and prouder of what we built.</p>
            <div class="stats">
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <h3>6</h3>
                    <p>Members</p>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <h3>200+</h3>
                    <p>Hours of Coding</p>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <h3>Countless</h3>
                    <p>Cups of Coffee</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-section">
            <h2>Our Values</h2>
            <p>The principles that kept us going through this crazy project</p>
            <div class="values">
                <div class="value-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-code"></i>
                    <h3>Teamwork & Chaos</h3>
                    <p>We thrived in the chaos of group work—everyone coded, everyone argued, and somehow, we made it work.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="value-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-laptop-code"></i>
                    <h3>Learn by Doing</h3>
                    <p>From front-end to back-end, we learned by diving in headfirst, even if it meant breaking the app a few times.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="value-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-coffee"></i>
                    <h3>Late-Night Vibes</h3>
                    <p>Nothing beats the energy of coding at midnight with snacks, music, and a looming deadline.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-section">
            <h2>Meet Our Team</h2>
            <p>The brilliant (and slightly chaotic) minds behind CookHub</p>
            <div class="team">
                <div class="team-member">
                    <img src="../assets/image/lyna.png" alt="Ly Na">
                    <h3>Ly Na</h3>
                    <p>Team Leader</p>
                    <p>Our fearless leader who kept us on track (and fed us with her famous bánh mì recipe).</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-member">
                    <img src="../assets/image/sohyun.JPG" alt="Sohyun">
                    <h3>Sohyun</h3>
                    <p>Front-End Wizard</p>
                    <p>Obsessed with pixel-perfect designs—once spent 3 hours debating a button color.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-member">
                    <img src="../assets/image/xuan.jpg" alt="Xuân Bùi">
                    <h3>Xuân Bùi</h3>
                    <p>Back-End Master</p>
                    <p>Our database guru who also secretly loves designing UI (but won’t admit it).</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-member">
                    <img src="../assets/image/giang.jpg" alt="Giang Claude">
                    <h3>Giang Claude</h3>
                    <p>Design & Code Enthusiast</p>
                    <p>The team’s artist who coded front-end and back-end while doodling food sketches.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-member">
                    <img src="../assets/image/huyentrang.jpg" alt="Huyền Trang">
                    <h3>Huyền Trang</h3>
                    <p>Back-End Pro</p>
                    <p>Fixed bugs faster than we could find them, and kept us laughing with her witty comments.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-member">
                    <img src="../assets/image/lan.jpg" alt="Ngọc Lan">
                    <h3>Ngọc Lan</h3>
                    <p>Database Queen</p>
                    <p>Made our database run like magic while sneaking in some front-end fixes on the side.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- End: About Us Content -->

    <!-- Begin: Footer -->
    <div class="footer"></div>
    <!-- End: Footer -->
</body>
</html>